<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">很简单<br><br>题主首先需要的是......一群广场舞大妈<br><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/e9c451b7dd1d3ed0c1a64354401085e7_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="369" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="550" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/e9c451b7dd1d3ed0c1a64354401085e7_r.jpg"><br><br><br>其次需要的是....<br><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/86c76a718c3eb4441a8289cd76658538_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="787" data-rawheight="624" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="787" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/86c76a718c3eb4441a8289cd76658538_r.jpg"><br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>..<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>把这两者结合在一起，将产生史上最强扰民....啊不对...表白神器！！！<br><img data-rawheight="369" data-rawwidth="550" src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/ce3388f117f7d370215f85f57de3e3f1_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="550" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/ce3388f117f7d370215f85f57de3e3f1_r.jpg"><br>碉堡了有木有！！！再也不需苦哈哈地趴在地上摆蜡烛了有木有！！！还附带广场音乐BGM！！！妹子想注意不到都难！！！！！<br><br>---------------------------------------------------<br>为了可爱的妹子们，已取匿  (╭ ╯3╰)╭♡
